result.name: administrative-spend-over-500-in-uk-trade-and-investment
result.notes:
A monthly-updated list of administrative financial transactions spending over £500 made by UK Trade and Investment, as part of the Government's commitment to transparency in expenditure.

From January 2016 both administration and programme spend are now collected under the same code so appear as a single spreadsheet. See https://data.gov.uk/dataset/uk-trade-and-investment-spend

organization.name: uk-trade-and-investment
organization.title: UK Trade and Investment
organization.description:
UKTI works with UK based businesses to ensure their success in international markets through exports. We encourage and support overseas companies to look at the UK as the best place to set up or expand their business.

http://www.gov.uk/ukti

result.title: Administrative spend over £500 in UK Trade and Investment
